TableContextTimeStampAfterTable: {68829=Complimenting the Agency Power rear suspension program, we have added a new set of adjustable rear sway bar links. These sway bar links work with the stock or after market sway bars and control arms. They are CNC machined 6061 aluminum centers with flats for easy adjustment. The sway bar links feature aluminum spacers to fit into the control arm which attach to a 3 piece spherical rod end. The spherical rod ends used on top and bottom feature a Teflon lining for longevity and a rattle free ride. Improving rigidity and function, these rear sway bar links are ideal for track users or those who want a show finish suspension. The Agency Power Rear Adjustable Sway Bar Links fit the 2008 and up Subaru WRX STI GH and GE models.}
